snippet.description:
The official YouTube channel of alt-J. Subscribe for the latest music videos, performances, and more.

After winning the Mercury Prize in 2012 with their debut album An Awesome Wave, Joe Newman [vocals, guitar], Gus Unger-Hamilton [vocals, keyboards, bass] and Thom Sonny Green [drums, percussion] made the Grammy-nominated This Is All Yours (2014) and followed it with Relaxer (2017). 

The Dream, alt-J’s fourth album, began life on schedule when the band first regrouped at their own studio, a rented house in east London where they write and record. Navigating Covid as it arrived and hung around – with Green shielding throughout the pandemic and often working remotely, The Dream was recorded from August 2020 until June 2021 with long-time producer Charlie Andrew. What emerged was a record of intrigue and ambiguity that fizzes with a rejuvenated sense of experimentalism. 

The new album The Dream is out now : https://alt-j.lnk.to/thedreamID
snippet.title: alt-J

snippet.description:
Les Mineurs du son vous font découvrir le meilleur du Trip Hop : Trip-Hop, Downtempo, Abstract Hip-Hop, Electro Jazz, Chillout...

The Minors of the sound make you discover the best of Trip Hop : Trip-Hop, Downtempo, Abstract Hip-Hop, Electro Jazz, Chillout...

Envie de nouveautés, de découvertes et d'inspirations musicales ?? Ne cherchez plus, les « Mineurs Du Son » sont là pour vous !! Né de la rencontre et surtout de l'amitié de deux lillois, grands fans de Musique (avec un grand M), le projet des « Mineurs Du Son » se construit petit à petit depuis 2007, autour d'une même philosophie : partager et diffuser au plus grand nombre le meilleur du Trip-Hop... Attention, ne nous arrêtons pas à une simple appellation, le Trip-Hop est un style musical très éclectique, aux frontières certes très floues, mais surtout aux inspirations multiples et au potentiel illimité : Electro-jazz, Abstract Hip-Hop, Instrumental, Post-Rock, Ambient, Chill-Out, Experimental, Downtempo, Nu-Jazz, Breakbeat, Turntablism... Laissez-vous surprendre et venez voyager avec les « pépites » spécialement découvertes pour vous, par les « Mineurs Du Son ». Et évidemment, cela va sans dire, notre objectif n'est pas commercial. Il s'agit, modestement, de vous faire découvrir et de vous permettre de partager avec vos amis, un panel varié et diversifié de musique Trip-Hop : nous fouinons, farfouillons et creusons toutes les pistes sonores qui s'offrent à nous, pour dénicher les meilleurs morceaux du moment (mais aussi les classiques du genre) ! Alors, n'hésitez plus, laissez-vous guider et suivez les posts des « Mineurs Du Son » et surtout diffusez autour de vous : car rappelez-vous, la musique et le bonheur qu'elle procure n'a lieu d'être que si elle est partagée !
snippet.title: MineurDuSon

snippet.description:
About me:
My name is David James Armsby. I was born in May 1996, in Scotland.
I was homeschooled and spent all my teen years inside, learning new skills and working on elaborate projects. This is when I learned to animate, draw, paint, sculpt, make films, etc.
All my animation and film-making skills are self-taught. I started animating in 2012, and through a monumental amount of trial and error; I managed to learn how to create original films on my own.
I went to study 'Art and Design' at my local college in 2015 covering fine art, still life, basic drawing skills, and sculpture. I had to start at the bottom of the academic ladder because of my lack of formal qualifications. I was far beyond what they were teaching, but I was going more so for the social and life experience. The one thing college taught me was the importance of sketchbooks, which has since become a huge part of my creative process.

I left college in 2019 and have since made Youtube/Patreon my full-time job.
snippet.title: Dead Sound

snippet.description:
byron play some sort of rock music since 2006, releasing 7 studio albums and 3 live DVDs in the meantime. Equally comfortable with loud amps or no amps at all, they filmed a gig in a salt mine (100m below) just to show they mean business, they composed the soundtrack for an HBO series in their home country and they played live as far as India. 

byron's seventh studio album „Nouă”, released in November 2019, is a political statement that shares light on the emigration crisis Romania is facing today and provokes the listener to engage in a dialogue. The album consists of twelve melodic and anthemic songs seasoned with plenty of distorted guitars, skillful piano and breathtaking vocals.

2022 has byron working on new songs for a new album, due in autumn. 

line-up:
Dan Byron - vocals, guitar, flute
Sergiu "6" Mitrofan - keyboards, vocals
Dan Georgescu - guitar, vocals
Laszlo Demeter - bass guitar, bass synth

snippet.description: Formed in the late '90s by friends and bandmates Josh Rosenfeld and Christopher Possanza as a way to put out music by their own band (This Busy Monster) and by their friends (Death Cab for Cutie, John Vanderslice, et al), Barsuk Records has grown and flourished over the years to release classic indie records from other Northwest artists including The Long Winters, Laura Gibson, David Bazan, Chris Staples, Hibou, Rocky Votolato, Jesse Sykes & The Sweet Hereafter, Say Hi, Menomena, and Ruler, as well as Phantogram, Nada Surf, Ra Ra Riot, Charly Bliss, Maps & Atlases, Mates of State, The Dismemberment Plan, Rilo Kiley, Cymbals Eat Guitars, Common Holly, and more. Twenty plus years on, Barsuk is still run full-time by its owners and a small group of music-loving staffers. Focused not on any specific genre, but simply on supporting creativity, Barsuk has developed an outstanding reputation for quality and integrity, and the label promises to be a bastion of quality music for years to come.

snippet.description:
'New Battles' is an epic album, "album" as in the truest sense of the word and which you can also perceive to be a handheld theatre play. Like rhetoric goth, the lyrics read like pamphlets. The wording is straight and simple in its striving for a better world. Pennyblackmusic (UK)

In my opinion, 2L8 with "New Battles without Honor and Humanity" will produce a small cult of fans among the avant-garde and indie rock music. I admit it, I am a little surprised that this band is still not known everywhere. Machinist (Belarus)

2L8 are indescribable. They manage to convey the sound of today. 2L8 are the culmination of contemporary musical expression, a sound document that we must listen "to understand how music evolves". Alter Ars (Spain)

Led by K the Clown, the ever-fluctuating group 2L8 has produced two albums of heady avant garde explorations, pop, rock, and glorious dissonance.Listen to the epic, irresistible, oddball violin and poetry-dominated music that they make. MTV Iggy
snippet.title: 2L8
